1. Make sure you Restart Hadoop cluster

sudo service hadoop-master stop
sudo service hadoop-master start
hadoop dfsadmin -safemode leave

2. Command: Hive --service metastore 
-- Only edureka machine. You can omit in cloudera vm or realtime

3. COmmand: hive --service hiveserver -p 10000 &  
--> Run this command before running this prog. It will take time to start
-- Make sure that port is 10000 in java file. change ports in both places if errors are present

4. Follow link and also see how to use hive2
http://saurzcode.in/2015/01/connect-hiveserver2-service-jdbc-client/
